# IAM GitHub — OAuth Write + SSH Git (SamPrimeaux)

## OAuth connected agents (ChatGPT MCP, in-app)

**`agentsam_github_write`** now uses **`upsert_file`**:

| Case | What to pass |
|------|----------------|
| **New file** | `path`, `content`, `message`, `repo` — **omit `sha`** |
| **Update existing** | Same + optional `sha` from prior `agentsam_github_read` |

Do **not** pass `sha: ""` — omit the field entirely for creates.

**Read/discover:** `agentsam_github_read`, `agentsam_github_repo_list`

## Terminal git — all Sam repos (Sam / `ws_inneranimalmedia`)

PTY has **no `gh` CLI**. Use `agentsam_terminal_run` for multi-file work:

| Pattern | Remote |
|---------|--------|
| Any `SamPrimeaux/REPO` | `git@github.com:SamPrimeaux/REPO.git` |
| `inneranimalmedia-mcp-server` only | `git@github.com-inneranimal-mcp:SamPrimeaux/inneranimalmedia-mcp-server.git` |

```bash
git clone git@github.com:SamPrimeaux/YOUR-REPO.git
# ... edit multiple files ...
git add -A && git commit -m "feat: scaffold" && git push origin HEAD
```

SSH host aliases on PTY: `github.com`, `github-inneranimal`, `github.com-inneranimal-mcp`, `github.com-agentsam`.

## Connor / other users

Each user configures **`workspace_settings.github`** on their own workspace. Do not assume Sam's `SamPrimeaux` remotes.

